Download the tarbal from: https://github.com/bat/bat/releases/download/v1.0.0-RC1/BAT-1.0.0-RC1.tar.gz
gunzip and/or untar.
cd into the directiory
copy files in BATv1.0_parallel-dev/BAT-dev to BAT-1.0.0-RC1/BAT
copy files in BATv1.0_parallel-dev/src-dev to BAT-1.0.0-RC1/src
./configure --prefix=path CXX=mpic++
make
make install

FOR GCC 5+
./configure --prefix=path CXX=mpic++
